<p><strong>えいごで:</strong> <em>Kichijoji</em> is the number one place where people in Japan wish to live. This charming neighbourhood has many small shops and borders on <em>Inakoshira</em> park.</p>

<p><strong>Japanese:</strong> いのこしらおんしこうえん</p>

